                <s type="roman">ŋis-enok-il iōansē kolistantinopol-in arkhēepiskobos-a-denal on akil
                    ŋapi-ko-a-denan-na istaurosou ŋok-kon-k-in orōse-n sal-a-lo till-in
                    tōkinaue-loko amēn</s>
                <s type="gloss">holy-COMP-DET John Constantinople-GEN, archbishop-PRED-CONJ and mouth
                    gold-ADJ-PRED-CONJ-GEN cross glory-ADJ-?-GEN praise-GEN word-PRED-FOC God-GEN
                    peace-LOC.through amen</s>
                <s type="trans" xml:lang="eng">‘(This is the word) of praise of the Holy Cross of
                    the holiest John, Archbishop of Constantinople and golden-mouthed. Through the
                    peace of God, Amen.’</s>
                <note/>
