            <ab xml:id="SC3">
                <s type="orig">ⲟⲛⲧⲁⲕⲣⲁⲅⲟⲩⲉ̄ⲕⲉ ⲙⲛⲁ ⲗ̣̄ⲇⲛ̄ⲛⲉ· ⲙⲛⲁ ⲡⲉⲥⲁⲣⲣⲉ·</s>
                <s type="parse">ⲟⲛ-ⲧⲁⲕ-ⲣ-ⲁ-ⲅⲟⲩⲉ-̄ⲕⲉ ⲙ-ⲛⲁ ⲗ-̄ⲇⲛ̄ⲛⲉ ⲙⲛⲁ ⲡⲉⲥ-ⲁⲣ-ⲣ-ⲉⲣⲉ·</s>
                <s type="roman">on-tak-r-a-goue-ke mn-a il-d-in-n-e mn-a pes-ar-r-e</s>
                <s type="gloss">love-PASS-PRS-PRED-PL.PRED-2PL what-QUOT say-INTEN-CAP-PRS-1SG.PRED
                    what-QUOT say-INTEN-PRS-1SG.PRED</s>
                <s type="trans" xml:lang="eng">‘Beloved! What could I say? What shall I speak?’</s>
                <note>Notes The scribe misinterprets aorist subjunctive lalήsw as future indicative,
                    translating with ⲡⲉⲥⲁⲣⲣⲉ.</note>
            </ab>
            <ab xml:id="SC4">
                <s type="orig">ⳟⲁⲉⲓⲁ̄ ⲟⲩⲕ ⲟ̄ⲕⲓⳝⲁⲣⲣⲉ·</s>
